{"tid":612351,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"del msg 其實岩唔岩","createTime":"2018-03-31T18:41:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T04:39:01.000Z","uid":69942,"like":33,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9fe8345282cc8307c9a86837cc72bebfaa5376a1","tid":612351,"uid":69942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:41:43.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n今日我返工無聊得制，聊左個識左十幾年既女性朋友傾計，傾唔夠兩句都佢都冇乜心覆我，我自尊心受創加上唔想比女朋友擔心我花fit，所以我先決定del msg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仆街之後同女朋友食緊飯既時候佢又突然覆返我wo,女友即刻問邊個來 跟住搶埋我手機發現我曾經del msg 發牌氣嬲到叫分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外，之前我都試過del msg因為同男圈子傾埋哂d叫雞屌西既話題（我從未叫過雞）由於太麻甩既關係先del msg，果陣已經嬲過一次我del msg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但我既睇法就係，del msg既出法點都係為女朋友好，我又冇做過咩對唔住佢既<br />\n事，問返我做咩del msg, msg 內容係咩我一定答佢 ，有需要發牌氣咩? <br />\n<br />\ndel msg =錯死罪正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\ndel 咪del 對得住女友對得住自己咪得 負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4186e297bef6bfd089c2e6b24f09202f8f6afc3d","tid":612351,"uid":12570,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:50:49.000Z","msg":"del msg係冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n錯在你比女朋友發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e0d66509d8bdab31f33b3e155957b66503afcf8","tid":612351,"uid":90615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T18:51:47.000Z","msg":"無乜咪唔好del<br />\ndel左就好心唔好比人發現"},{"pid":"0f028a152dd12cf56f486c2ef8a3ad2b84f11834","tid":612351,"uid":68864,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T19:17:33.000Z","msg":"為乜女朋友好呀<img src=\"/